dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Willie Clark. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Samantha. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Yes, my policy number is five two three four six.
Thank you, Samantha. Additionally, could you verify your date of birth for security purposes?
Sure, my date of birth is the twenty-second of December, nineteen seventy-eight.
Thank you for confirming, Samantha. Is there anything specific I can assist you with today?
I would like to add a new vehicle to my policy.
I can help you with that request. Let's proceed with the vehicle details. Shall we?
Thank you for your time, Samantha. If you need further assistance, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
